                            between technology and environmental responsibility. We aim to become the most trusted
                            companion to every business in India.</p>
                        <a href="/services" class="btn"
                            style="padding: 18px 45px; border-radius: 50px; background: #29abe2; color: white; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.1rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(41,171,226,0.3); transition: all 0.3s ease;">Explore
                            Services</a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Right Graphic (Main Founder Redesign) -->
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div style="position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                            <div class="main-founder-card"
                                style="position: relative; z-index: 2; background: #ffffff; padding: 2.2rem; border-radius: 40px; border: 4px solid rgba(155, 207, 90, 0.4); box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(155, 207, 90, 0.15), 0 0 20px rgba(155, 207, 90, 0.1); width: 100%; max-width: 400px; transition: transform 0.4s ease;">
                                <div
                                    style="width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 1/1; border-radius: 25px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                                    <img src="/images/main founder.jpeg" alt="EonMove Founder"
                                        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;">
                                </div>
                                <div style="text-align: center;">
                                    <h4 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 950; color: #1e293b; margin-bottom: 8px;">
